name: StudySensei
description: StudySensei combines AI and human insights to create personalized study schedules on Notion. Using GPT-3.5, Weaviate, and the Notion API, it tailors plans to your study time and goals. Future enhancements include a website/app, a scheduling chatbot, and advanced multi-course management.

name: RicAI Autonomous Testing Agent
description: Autonomous AI Agent is developed to streamline software testing by understanding complex requirements, generating test cases, conducting unit, usability, and acceptance tests (using tools like Selenium), and providing detailed feedback and reports.

name: IGT - Image Generator Tester
description: The Image Generator Tester (IGT) integrates Weaviate and DALL-E-2, enabling users to generate multiple prompts or images from one. It serves as an Image-Based AI Tester, helping developers evaluate AI models in image recognition and generation, fostering continuous improvement and deeper understanding of image generation technologies.

name: Remote Patriot
description: RemotePatriot.com revolutionizes remote work for disabled veterans with personalized LLM autonomous agents that match them to jobs, handle applications, and communicate with hiring managers. Founded by a Marine, it offers AI-driven, empowering job search experiences and autonomous recruitment for employers.

name: MoodTune MelodyBot
description: MoodTune MelodyBot is an empathetic AI that enhances musical connections by understanding users' emotions. Unlike typical music recommendation engines, it provides personalized playlists that resonate with individual feelings, offering a heartfelt and human-like interaction that bridges technology and emotion.

name: Intention Engine
description: Intention Engine optimizes user-centric experiences over engagement metrics, ensuring content relevance and privacy. Its autonomous chatbot clarifies and updates user intentions in real-time, creating personalized experiences. With a secure REST API for third-party integration, it provides a compliant, privacy-focused alternative in the evolving digital landscape.

name: PRPioneer Auto Code Reviewer
description: PRPioneer Auto Code Reviewer introduces a game-changing tool for code reviews, streamlining feedback with concise summaries and detailed reports. Integrated with the @semantic-labs chatbot, it fosters dynamic Q&A sessions for clarity and knowledge sharing. Simple integration via AMICUS.json transforms the code review landscape, enhancing collaboration and efficiency.

name: Odoo AI Store
description: Odoo AI Store facilitates text-based shopping without internet using LangChain React Agent and GPT-4. It analyzes user queries, retrieves products from Weavite Vector DB, and employs Odoo API or Google to assist in purchasing. This technology extends beyond Odoo, benefiting e-commerce for users with limited internet access.

name: TAix - Tax Advice Agent
description: TAiX simplifies tax management for freelancers and businesses with automated accounting. Using Weaviate index and layoutlm-invoices, TAiX Agent handles calculations and regulatory tracking, eliminating manual errors. Accessible via a user-friendly Streamlit app, TAiX promises hassle-free tax management, making it more enjoyable than ever.

name: Shop Fusion AI - your new shopping buddy
description: Shop Fusion AI enhances eCommerce with personalized experiences, offering outfit recommendations and efficient checkout management. For users, it's like having a personal stylist. For store owners, it ensures seamless transactions and customer satisfaction through automated support.

name: Arkimedes
description: Arkimedes, powered by Cohere, connects enterprises with global talent. Accessible via mobile and web, it streamlines job discovery for users and facilitates enterprise-talent engagement. Key features include niche job searches, turbo semantic search, and personal AI career agents, all integrated into a seamless Telegram bot interface. Built for AI Founders/Radical Ventures Hackathon 2024.

name: InSight
description: 'Insight' innovates research with LLM, RAG, Weaviate, and Langchain, simplifying knowledge discovery. Users interact via Cohere for effective query processing. LangChain orchestrates text tasks, and Weaviate organizes research data. This project bridges the gap between users and research content, enhancing information retrieval intuitively.

name: connectED
description: ConnectED serves as a centralized platform for health updates, connecting government agencies and NGOs. SMS functionality ensures accessibility, benefiting remote areas. It disseminates advisories on outbreaks, medical practices, and vaccinations. By uniting information providers and citizens, ConnectED extends institutional messaging effectively, transcending traditional outreach limitations.

name: Multi-Lingual Customer Service Chat Assistance
description: Multi-Lingual Customer Service Chat Assistance, powered by Cohere AI, communicates seamlessly in English, German, and Italian. It handles queries and feedback efficiently, leveraging Weaviate's database and Langchain Technologies. Hosted on Streamlit, it revolutionizes global customer interactions with inclusive, efficient solutions for diverse businesses.

name: BYTE - AI-Based Nutrition App
description: Elevate your diet with our AI-Powered Nutrition App, offering personalized guidance based on health profiling and label analysis. Weaviate's database fuels customized dietary advice. Coral, our chatbot, suggests healthier alternatives. Streamlined interface and robust security ensure a seamless user experience.

name: QuickScore-an AI Grader
description: AutograderX: Revolutionizing Education with advanced autograding leveraging RAG and LLMs. Addressing grading challenges, it automates evaluations, reducing educator workload and errors. Immediate feedback enhances student engagement, promising to transform academic evaluation and promote faster progress in education.

name: RAG Fusion with Cohere and Weaviate
description: RAG Fusion: Enhancing Query Variations generates and retrieves question variants, performing fusion and re-ranking for better matches. Synthetic data enrichment and LangChain aid in processing. Resulting queries are augmented using co.chat, presented in a customized UI. Future plans include UX enhancements and PaLM2 integration for harmful content protection.

name: Drug Discovery Assistant
description: 'Drug Discovery Assist: Streamlining Research' offers a unified interface to explore arXiv's latest research in quantitative biology. It enables search and summarization of research papers and drug information, easing the burden of manual searches. This platform facilitates quick access to cutting-edge research and drug insights for researchers.

name: Tadabor
description: Tadabor employs Weaviate and Cohere's text2vec embeddings to streamline reflection on Quranic verses. With Ibn Kathir Tafsir, it offers scholarly insights, while Cohere's Gen AI and Langchain simplify verses and generate reflective questions for a deeper engagement with the sacred text.

name: Chat with Your Football Scouter
description: Utilizing 2022-2023 Football Player Stats from Kaggle, the 'Football Player Stats Analyzer' project covers extensive player data across top leagues. Leveraging Cohere Embedding and Weaviate Cloud Service, features like Chat and Compare Player employ advanced language models for nuanced insights into player performances with Retrieval-augmented Generation techniques.

name: Market AI
description: Market AI: Streamlined Hedge Fund Management. Seamlessly navigate stock data with cutting-edge technologies like Cohere, Langchain, and Weaviate. Access company filings, monitor portfolios, and execute real-time trades. Tailored for investors, this chat experience simplifies research and decision-making, ensuring agile investment management.

name: PyLibrarian
description: Pylibrarian empowers developers with complete Python library documentation accessible via ChatGPT. Built with RAG architecture, Pylibrarian leverages Cohere's embedding and Weaviate's vector database for semantic search, ensuring accurate responses. Say goodbye to wasted hours searching for syntax examples‚ÄîPylibrarian provides consistent, grounded solutions.

name: herechat
description: Herechat is a chatbot designed to transform digital communication, particularly within online communities like Discord. It's built from a robust dataset of top-tier Reddit responses and is meticulously crafted to engage, understand, and respond with unprecedented relevance and wit.

name: Climate Impact with STS
description: Climate Impact with STS is a project that integrates climate action documents and technologies like Weaviate, Cohere, and potentially others. It aims to provide users with an immersive experience focused on addressing climate-related challenges, potentially involving tasks such as research, analysis, and collaboration within the realm of climate action and sustainability.

name: Propulsion
description: Propulsion revolutionizes AEC Proposal Development. It offers a tailored solution for Architecture, Engineering, and Construction (AEC) firms, easing repetitive project matching and proposal writing challenges. Integrating Cohere‚Äôs Coral, Embeddings, and Weaviate‚Äôs Vector Database, it streamlines proposal creation with data-driven insights, fostering efficiency and competitiveness.

name: Dionysus
description: Dionysus streamlines developer collaboration. With automatic code documentation, AI-powered commit message summaries, and real-time meeting transcription, developers can efficiently collaborate. Built on a microservices architecture with GitHub integration and CohereAI's tools, Dionysus ensures scalability and productivity.

name: Weaviate Blogs QA Chatbot prototype
description: Weaviate Blogs QA Chatbot Prototype offers a user-friendly interface for accessing Weaviate's 2023 blog content. Powered by LangChain for rapid prototyping and Cohere's reranker for optimal search results, it combines semantic and keyword search for an enhanced user experience. Future plans include a frontend UI and feedback loops for continuous improvement.

name: OrbChat - Always-On Support for your Website
Pipegen AI
description: Pipegen streamlines the creation of Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG) models with a no-code platform. Its intuitive wizard enables users to effortlessly generate and fine-tune custom models for diverse applications, eliminating the need for advanced programming skills. Pipegen offers flexibility and accessibility across sectors, democratizing RAG technology.

name: Phil AI
description: Phil AI is your personal Philanthropy assistant. It simplifies charitable giving by leveraging Cohere and Weaviate. It matches your interests with impactful charity projects, ensuring alignment with your values. With Phil AI, you're not just donating; you're investing in causes that resonate with you personally, making a meaningful difference.

name: MedCoderAI
description: MediCode serves a an 'intelligent medical coding partner' revolutionizes coding accuracy with RAG technology via LangChain and Weaviate. Accessing up-to-date CMS ICD-10 and CPT codes, it streamlines billing and care. Say goodbye to clunky interfaces; collaborate seamlessly with an AI partner, suggesting accurate codes and enhancing efficiency in real-time.
types: TruEra Challenge: Build LLM Applications Summary

name: Nivx Voice Multi Modal Digital Shopping Assistant
description: Nivx AI is an innovative tool designed to enhance the online shopping experience by offering personalized assistance, product recommendations, and clothing suggestions to customers. It utilizes advanced technology like Multi Modal Gemini Pro and RAG models and integrates seamlessly with Shopify stores via Next.js 14.

name: WikiSearch
description: WikiSearch uses Weaviate for semantic search over Wikipedia articles. With Cohere, it summarizes results. Just add your Cohere API Key for enhanced functionality.

name: YouTube Q and A
description: Get summaries of any YouTube video, ask questions about the topics in the video, and see the source of the response

name: ClipSift
description: ClipSift is a tool for you to automatically speed up content / asset searching. By providing a natural lanaguage description, you can easily query the top relevant YouTube videos and get the most relevant clips to review. Copyrights reserved to the original creators of the videos.

name: DXC IT Fin Analytica AI
description: Fin-Analytica transforms financial analysis. Harnessing AI, it scrutinizes company finances, providing actionable insights via an integrated chatbot. Investors find opportunities, businesses enhance profitability, and students deepen financial knowledge with context-driven analysis and recommendations. Your ultimate financial companion.

name: Astronomer: Zephyr - an AI Agent for Apache Airflow
description: Zephyr is a hypervisor-like agent for Apache Airflow instances built by Astronomer. It consists of an API, an AI agent, and a UI. We store previous errors, along with their successful resolutions, in Weaviate. Zephyr will automatically detect your pipeline and task failures, and when it does so, the AI agent attempts to fix it.

name: Teradata TechStorm AI Virtual Assistant
description: Teradata TechStorm AI Assistant bridges AI and productivity for terminal developers. Powered by Cohere's conversational AI, Weaviate's semantic search, and LangChain's text/image processing, it delivers intuitive, personalized experiences. With direct calls to Yahoo! Finance for real-time stock quotes, it's a comprehensive tool for efficient workflow enhancement.

name: SECSavvyNow
description: SecSavvyNow delivers tailored financial insights from critical documents like 10-Ks, catering to individual investors, financial analysts, and enterprise sales teams. It empowers investors with actionable insights, equips analysts with precise data, and gives sales teams a competitive edge, enhancing decision-making across finance and investment sectors.

name: Crest Data Systems: Security AI Assistant
ConscienceOS Biomimicry-inspired Design Decisions
description: ConscienceOS integrates Biomimicry principles, leveraging the AskNature dataset, to emulate nature's problem-solving strategies. Through Semantic and Hybrid Search, it guides users in applying nature's wisdom to address challenges. By aligning design decisions with nature, ConscienceOS fosters sustainable and innovative solutions, bridging ancient wisdom with AI advancements.

name: Makers Tech Tree
description: Makers Tech Tree is an innovative resource inspired by MIT's 'How To Make (almost) Anything' course, covering diverse topics from 3D modeling to biology. It compiles information to generate insights, thriving on user queries. Designed for makers, it envisions integration with cloud labs and 3D printer farms, refining pipelines and experiments.

name: Internship Finder
description: Internship Finder is a web app revolutionizing internship searches. Upload your resume for analysis, extracting key details. It then matches you with relevant opportunities, offering an interactive interface to explore and apply seamlessly. Tailored to your resume, it simplifies the hunt for your ideal internship.

name: Oraculum
description: Oraculum is AI assistant designed to answer questions using a knowledge base. Leveraging Weaviate's vector database, it indexes information semantically for multilingual querying. Facts, categorized with metadata, form prompts for Sibylla, the chat assistant. Powered by PowerShell cmdlets, it spiders and adds knowledge from various sources, enhancing interaction and learning.

name: RecipeMate
description: RecipeMate is a user-friendly, ad-free recipe search platform available on iOS, Android, and web. Utilizing AI vector search, it tailors recipes to your taste, pantry, diet, and allergies. Save, manage, and adjust servings, with nutrition facts available. As a progressive web app, it's easily installable. Feedback and downloads appreciated.

name: Unbody.io
description: Unbody.io simplifies AI integration into apps and websites. Originally a headless CMS, it migrated its database to Weaviate, becoming the first CMS on a vector database. Unbody automates AI pipelines, integrates data, and offers AI functions via GraphQL or SDKs, democratizing advanced AI for developers without deep expertise.

name: Findr
description: Findr aggregates scattered information from various apps like Slack, Notion, and Gmail into a single search bar. Powered by Weaviate, it enables effortless access to links, documents, and more, saving time wasted on searching across different platforms.

name: VoxGig Podcast Chatbot
description: Voxgig has the tools and expertise to help you maximize your developer relations efforts. Our proven tools for developer advocates and conference organizers can help you get the most out of your knowledge, time, and audience, no matter the size of your organization. Let us help you maximize your impact and achieve your goals.

name: Duckie.ai
description: Duckie is an AI technical support engineer that reduces unnecessary ticket escalations by troubleshooting and resolving tricky technical issues. Integrated into support channels, it intelligently handles requests, leveraging knowledge bases to provide insights and only escalating to developers when necessary, streamlining support processes and minimizing costs.

name: Visual Aid
description: Visual AId pioneers AI-driven cosmetic surgery prediction and visualization. It offers predictive outcomes, assisting surgeons with surgical guidance and enabling collaborative validation. With a focus on precision outcomes, it leverages deep learning and generative AI techniques, aiming to revolutionize cosmetic surgery worldwide for improved accessibility and personalization.

name: Caramel Horse
description: Caramel Horse is a platform that utilizes AI to help reconnect pet owners with their lost pets through photos. By analyzing images of lost pets uploaded by users, the platform employs AI algorithms to match them with potential sightings or found pets, facilitating their safe return home.
